Waleɲumandɔn ni foliw.
David Werner de ye nin gafe in sɛbɛnbaga fɔlɔ ye ɛsipaɲɔli ni angilɛkan na.
A ka hakilinata, a ŋaniya ni a ka cɛsiri nɔ yelen don gafe in ɲɛ kelen kelen bɛɛ la.
Segin kɛlen gafe in kan, Carol Thuman ani Jane Maxwell ye u cɛsiri ɲinini ni a sɛbɛnni ani a labɛnni fɛ.
An bɛ u waleɲumandɔn u ka baara ɲuman ni u ka ŋaniya ɲuman na.
Nin gafe in kɔnɔko fanba bɔra gafe wɛrɛ la min sɛbɛnna senegali baarada dɔ fɛ min tɔgɔ ko ENDA-Tiers-Monde.
