Walikan kalan ye fanga sɔrɔ kosɛbɛ, nka halisa, an ka togoda yɔrɔ dɔw bɛ ye, o lakɔli kalan ma sabati yɔrɔ minnu na kosɛbɛ. O yɔrɔ ninnu bɛɛ la, i bɛ se ka mɔgɔ damadɔ sɔrɔ yen minnu b’u magow bɛɛ ɲɛnabɔ an fakanw na.
