Alzeri jamana la, Ali Bɛnn Fis, ni ale tùn ye Abdul Aziz Butefilika ka fàdenma, Alzeri jamanatigiya kalafili laban na, ye i Sèndon opposition (fanga-sinamatɔn) jɛ̀kulu la, min ye jamanatigi Weele ko a ka fanga Blà.
